## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="fcf7b-104">다음 예제를 만드는 방법을 보여 줍니다.는 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 변수를 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 개체 및 해당 할당을를 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> 의 속성을 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> 개체.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fcf7b-104">The following example shows the creation of an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and its assignment to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>  
  
```  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
